deactivateFromRegistry().details: Only owner can callDeactivate means:      - Stop accepting new gas payment requests      - Continue processing existing transactions (settlement)      - Continue unstake process if initiatedComplete exit flow:      1. deactivate()  isActive = false      2. Wait for all transactions to settle      3. unstake()  unlock stake      4. withdrawStake()  withdraw ETH, complete exitNote: Reactivation is controlled by Registry (requires qualification check)
